Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wit is your weapon{honestly no clue what is megurase here, deepl says "rack one's brain"}\NRemember to use your head{智恵をめぐらせ 頭を使え}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Repress your anguish, \NIf you are a man{悩み抜け抜け 男なら}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One decision is enough \NTo make others cry or laugh{泣くも笑うも 決断ひとつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win, don't hold your head high, \NIf you lose, don't cry{勝っておごるな 敗れて泣くな}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, don't you ever let other see your tears{男 涙は見せぬもの}
