Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.51,0:24:08.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Pacific War taught us the preciousness of peace. \NBut also instilled numerous lessons on how to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to ensure a surprise landing \Non the Malay peninsula,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the Japanese set their sights on Britain's famed \Nunsinkable battleship Prince of Wales,
